'''马丁·海雷尔'''（{{lang-de|'''Martin Hairer'''}}，{{bd|1975年|11月14日}}），[[奥地利|奥地利]][[数学家|数学家]]。其主要研究领域是[[随机分析|随机分析]]，尤其是[[随机偏微分方程|随机偏微分方程]]。他早年就读于[[日内瓦大学|日内瓦大学]]，2001年获博士学位。他现在是[[华威大学|华威大学]]教授，之前曾任[[纽约大学|纽约大学]]教职<ref>{{cite journal|title=Uniqueness of the Invariant Measure¶for a Stochastic PDE Driven by Degenerate Noise|journal=Communications in Mathematical Physics|doi=10.1007/s002200100424|url=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s002200100424|date=2001-06-01|volume=219|issue=3|language=en|pages=523–565|issn=0010-3616|accessdate=2018-04-03|author=J.-P. Eckmann, M. Hairer|archive-date=2018-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180609155834/https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s002200100424|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="scopus">{{Scopus|id=6602190457}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|url=http://annals.math.princeton.edu/2006/164-3/p07|pages=993–1032|title=Ergodicity of the 2D Navier–Stokes equations with degenerate stochastic forcing|journal=Annals of Mathematics|volume=164|issue=3|date=2006|issn=0003-486X|language=en-US|accessdate=2018-04-03|doi=10.4007/annals.2006.164.993|author=Martin Hairer, Jonathan Mattingly|archive-date=2018-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180603030752/http://annals.math.princeton.edu/2006/164-3/p07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年，他获得[[菲尔兹奖|菲尔兹奖]]。<ref name=imu>{{cite web|url=http://www.mathunion.org/general/prizes/2014/|title=IMU Prizes 2014|date=12 August 2014|accessdate=12 August 2014|archive-date=2017-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171203031644/http://www.mathunion.org/general/prizes/2014|dead-url=no}}</ref>

